Dear Reader
I don't know you and you don't know me . Probably we are not even living in the same country.We look different You may be older than me or younger.We are just completely strangers.But there are a few things which connect us .We are Humans.We have emotions and feelings.A personality which defines us.And we are both on YouTube, searching for sad things,no matter What's going on in your life at the moment,you can do it! You can manage out of it,You will stay stronger because there are people who love you.And these people are worth it!!Yes we are strangers but not too away from each other to not say that you're great person.Because you are!I hope even if it's just one of you,that I could help or support you in a way.
This comment is for all the lonely people out there like me.Heaps of love xx .
